    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput><ref refid="namespaceRADSettings" kindref="compound">RADSettings</ref></computeroutput> is the public settings library for application configuration.</para>
<para>Core features:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>JSON and INI settings files.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>App/organization based default config paths.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Typed getters and setters for common scalar values.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Compatibility with <computeroutput><ref refid="classRADCore_1_1RADJsonValue" kindref="compound">RADCore::RADJsonValue</ref></computeroutput>. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
